Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.48,0:00:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.76,0:00:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏露你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.44,0:00:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 这怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.26,0:00:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点 夏露
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.44,0:00:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快叫医生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.42,0:01:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么那件事进行的如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.64,0:01:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 一切都还算顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.18,0:01:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差那最后的一步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一步先别使出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南非那边的企业
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.56,0:01:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也收购得很成功 也又再迈进一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.92,0:01:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不能掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来有计划安排出国的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点神经衰弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:01:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.10,0:02:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先给她好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏露 身体不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 请多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:12.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她关在房里做什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.74,0:02:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总有一天会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说收购汽车公司只是个幌子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上\N是想要南非大叶工业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是葛萝莉亚家的生产线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏露也受了相当的打击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再这样让夏露做下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 夏露怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽可不用知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:02:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那接下来怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只好找个能做夏露工作的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来支撑这个家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 你没这种才能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 是谁能做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我之外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那二人的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不知他们做得来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 他们有这个才能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也这么相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 我会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量别引起骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说你做不来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:04:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈她似乎很期望你和绮罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和绮罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你们两人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和葛萝莉亚家有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你当我们家的一家之主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么也愿意做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也愿意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要……会被看见的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我一个人静一静
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绮罗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是很有威严的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威严
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是说你是这家之主也是不正确的罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 你发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表面上是我支持这个家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那都是夏露的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么也做不来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你…打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绮罗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事我必须向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有隐藏的事未说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 你和盖鲁克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是葛萝莉亚家的\N指定继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你们和我们结合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们世代都会流有你的血统
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才跟我说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不想强迫你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你能够很自然的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会想起这个家时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有葛萝莉亚的血统
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:06:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姆里克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姆里克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体觉得如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姆里克斯 你有没有看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姆里克斯把你看做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他的母亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.94,0:07:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能会离开你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很喜欢你的味道嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看 别摸 别接近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电脑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:08:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微借用一下\N喂 别随便乱摸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了别碰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了啦 先交给我来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像我也流着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你们一样的血统
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一样的血统
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 一样的血统
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来的问题呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南非钻石工厂的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.94,0:08:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个工厂被一家大企业
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从中偷买股权\N要将其夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而政府也以紧急事件处理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么一回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然钻石产量减少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收入也将减半
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么是玛丽的话 会怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:09:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先减薪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再向当地政府
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚开始先这样摸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想吃吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个就像冰淇淋一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美她说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师一定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事我来做就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么玛丽我不行做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你问为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是一直都是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道雪希儿的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想把老师占为己有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪希儿这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里只有玛丽是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽的双亲早亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后吃了不少苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.74,0:11:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她自己什么也不说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她来到葛萝莉亚家后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不能让她去碰难过的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.71,0:11:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽这样没错但也不能一直把她关在温室里面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽她自己也想出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温室里起了大风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许那就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家的当家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没这兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别装傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是当的话 就有上亿的财产落入口袋里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去会怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是要财产呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是要女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要当这家之主的路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我似乎比你快了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绮罗好像也发觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然一脸不在乎的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有份 我也有份
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:13:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那才是最好的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真认真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有时也会夸奖人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中午很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中午
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪希儿说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.98,0:13:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师很怕雷电
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我来陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真温柔体贴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师下面的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做 会不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:09.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很漂亮 玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.36,0:15:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽好怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像自己不是自己的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽要改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改变
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:16:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师继续
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛 却觉得很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要到那去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就会改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钻石工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识南非当地一位很厉害的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去麻烦他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定有帮助的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.52,0:18:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是个好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说玛丽很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都愿意帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直想说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但大家却说 玛丽可以不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以没说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是南非的大总统
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…你说舞会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使你来拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在对葛萝莉亚家而言 是多重要的时期
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜雪儿夫人 玛丽她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了葛萝莉亚家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想做我做得到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是夏露的姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你能让玛丽照她的想法去做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再什么也帮不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师也会在身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.74,0:19:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和老师在一起的话什么都做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布敏先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正等您来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 是玛丽说要办宴会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个人的主意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绮罗那小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:20:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在打什么主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜雪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜雪儿你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你邀我来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么悠闲好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.70,0:20:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说矿场那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快被收购走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:21:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天邀请各位来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.06,0:21:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽葛萝莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是南非的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么他们会在这
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天从南非而来的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也到了现场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可伏克总统
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天谢谢你们邀请我到这来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.68,0:21:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上 今天我的心情十分的沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在我国的钻石产业
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占有一席之地的葛萝莉亚家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.36,0:21:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然听说会有关闭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那是奸商的恶性作法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那资金
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.98,0:22:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说是从布敏企业而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位到场来宾和葛萝莉亚家在我国的钻石产业一切如常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.28,0:22:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以维护钻石产业
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.26,0:22:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不让不肖奸商 在工矿区乱收购股权
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此我也保证绝不改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.74,0:22:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大总统
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.50,0:22:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.90,0:22:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.96,0:22:38.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了小姐你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.95,0:22:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.48,0:22:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事随时可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.66,0:22:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.16,0:22:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你这混蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.90,0:22:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你全盘说出的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.80,0:22:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.24,0:22:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请肃静
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.08,0:22:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是葛萝莉亚家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西我先保管了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.66,0:23:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我也要发表一件重大的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我订婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.18,0:23:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方是秋筱绮罗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被他赶上一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.00,0:23:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.90,0:23:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.48,0:23:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 请问一下 南非那件事 是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.09,0:23:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.08,0:23:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请告诉我们真相
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.66,0:24:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你说说现在的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.23,0:24:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.86,0:24:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葛萝莉亚家的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.90,0:24:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪希儿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.52,0:24:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绮罗先生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.82,0:24:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪希儿 对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.88,0:24:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.16,0:24:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪希儿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.92,0:24:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.96,0:24:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.88,0:24:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心动的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.92,0:24:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,有时也和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.64,0:24:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.94,0:24:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.94,0:24:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.52,0:24:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果老师不在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.05,0:25:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便做不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.02,0:25:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…都快不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.66,0:25:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没这回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.33,0:25:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.58,0:25:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不再是老师了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.02,0:25:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,订婚了 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.12,0:25:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.44,0:25:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.74,0:25:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都是我的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.00,0:25:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.34,0:25:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽姐姐 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.22,0:25:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.98,0:25:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也该休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.66,0:25:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.10,0:25:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把希望放在他们身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.08,0:26:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽她变了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.44,0:26:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.04,0:26:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好只是把她的才能给发挥出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.00,0:26:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让人高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.64,0:26:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.48,0:26:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让人得救
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.74,0:26:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.81,0:26:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她那种心肠来当葛萝莉亚的当家
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.55,0:26:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再适合也不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.55,0:26:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.08,0:26:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她让我的心 动了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.16,0:27:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你们
